---

<section class="section cta-section" id="download">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-card reveal-s">
      <div class="cta-shine" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="cta-orb" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="cta-inner">
        <h2 class="cta-title" data-i18n="cta.title">Pronto para comer melhor?</h2>
        <p class="cta-sub" data-i18n="cta.sub">
          Junta-te a quem já controla a nutrição com a MacroMath. Descarrega grátis e começa hoje.
        </p>

        <div class="store-row">
          <a href="#" class="store-btn" aria-label="Download on the App Store">
            <svg class="store-ic" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M12.152 6.896c-.948 0-2.415-1.078-3.96-1.04-2.04.027-3.91 1.183-4.961 3.014-2.117 3.675-.54 9.103 1.519 12.09 1.013 1.46 2.208 3.09 3.792 3.039 1.52-.065 2.09-.987 3.935-.987 1.831 0 2.35.987 3.96.948 1.637-.026 2.676-1.48 3.676-2.948 1.156-1.688 1.636-3.325 1.662-3.415-.039-.013-3.182-1.221-3.22-4.857-.026-3.04 2.48-4.494 2.597-4.559-1.429-2.09-3.623-2.324-4.39-2.376-2-.156-3.675 1.09-4.61 1.09zM15.53 3.83c.843-1.012 1.4-2.427 1.245-3.83-1.207.052-2.662.805-3.532 1.818-.78.896-1.454 2.338-1.273 3.714 1.338.104 2.715-.688 3.559-1.701"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="store-txt">
              <small data-i18n="cta.appsub">Descarregar na</small>
              <strong data-i18n="cta.app">App Store</strong>
            </span>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="store-btn" aria-label="Get it on Google Play">
            <svg class="store-ic" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M3.6 2.1a1 1 0 0 0-.5.88v18.04a1 1 0 0 0 .5.88l10.2-9.9z" fill="#4285F4"/>
              <path d="M17.9 8.1 13.8 5.7 3.6 2.1c-.13-.07 10.4 9.9 10.4 9.9z" fill="#34A853"/>
              <path d="m13.8 12 4.1 4.2 3.05-1.74c.86-.49.86-1.94 0-2.43L17.9 10.3z" fill="#FBBC05"/>
              <path d="M3.6 21.9 13.8 12l4.1 4.2-4.1 2.4z" fill="#EA4335"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="store-txt">
              <small data-i18n="cta.playsub">Disponível no</small>
              <strong data-i18n="cta.play">Google Play</strong>
            </span>
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-card {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: var(--r-2xl);
    background: #0E0E0E;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.10);
    padding: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 4.8rem) 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }
  .cta-shine {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -45% -10% auto;
    height: 90%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(255, 90, 31, 0.26), transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .cta-orb {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -140px;
    right: -90px;
    width: 320px;
    height: 320px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 90, 31, 0.14), transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .cta-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .cta-title { font-size: var(--fs-4xl); font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.03em; color: #fff; line-height: 1.1; }
  .cta-sub { font-size: var(--fs-lg); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.94); margin: 1rem auto 2rem; max-width: 500px; }

  .store-row { display: flex; gap: 0.9rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .store-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.65rem;
    padding: 0.62rem 1.25rem;
    min-width: 178px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: #000;
    color: #fff;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.28);
    transition: transform var(--t-fast), border-color var(--t-fast);
  }
  .store-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6); }
  .store-ic { flex-shrink: 0; color: #fff; }
  .store-txt { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; line-height: 1.18; }
  .store-txt small { font-size: 0.64rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.02em; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92); }
  .store-txt strong { font-size: 1.16rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }

</style>
